parameters:
Memimi: I don't want to meet anyone in this situation... but
as the student council president, I can't just skip school
and shut myself away. Ever since my true identity was
revealed, things have been chaotic... I must set an
example...

Despite being in a position like a slave to the citizens,
Memimi has her public face as the student council president,
and there is an order to the school. Even Orca Asparagus,
the mayor, has guaranteed her right to study, and it's
strictly forbidden for outsiders to enter the school and
give orders to Memimi...

Male Student: Ah, Shark Mountain-san... Is it okay for you
to come to school? It seems like you're going through a lot.

Memimi: Ah... from the same class... Okikun... um... sorry
for... all the noise... The people causing a commotion in
town have been strictly told not to enter the school, so
please focus on your studies without worry...

Memimi: (Okikun... He's from the same class, he's cheerful
and popular, and I talk to him a lot... But he's severely
addicted to social media and often tweets about me...)

Male Student: Don't worry about us! Aren't you quite
exhausted, Shark Mountain-san? I saw a bit of that event in
front of the station... you were crying, weren't you?

Male Student: Shark Mountain-san, if it's okay with you,
shall I ask everyone at school not to give you any lewd
orders? I have many friends and owe favors to a lot of
people, so I think they'll listen to me.

Memimi: Eh...? Is that okay...? Indeed, even if we keep
those from outside the school out... I was considering the
possibility of receiving orders from the students...

Memimi's eyes widened in surprise. She had almost resigned
herself to the likelihood of facing terrible things at
school. If he could talk to the other students for her, then
for Memimi, the school could become a strong fortress
protecting her from shameful acts...

Memimi: I'm indebted to you... thank you...! Thank you,
Okikun... I've been really scared all this time...!! Thank
you... thank you so much, waaahhh...

Male Student: Yeah, yeah, so if you listen to what I say,
I'll negotiate with everyone for you. First, take off your
clothes and spread 'down there' like you did the other day?
